  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 058e9510505209449a5a210a4173157e, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  statementOne: A troglodyte could dodge better.
  statementTwo: I've seen more coordination in a bowl of noodles.
  statementThree: Sloths match your reaction time.
  statementFour: Lazy. Boring. Sloppy.
  statementFive: Lukewarm. Your score is lukewarm.
  statementSix: Ya did good; waiting for you to be great.
  statementSeven: You're starting to impress me .///.
  statementEight: The big leagues aren't calling just yet.
  statementNine: Ever considered going pro?
  statementTen: Herobrine ain't got NOTHING on you.
  label: {fileID: 1593501133}
